<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Since it's a functionality of PHP SoapClient, Zend_Soap_Client should accept 'user_agent' option.
Becareful that empty string for this option says to SoapClient to not send 'user_agent' header at all, thus Zend_Soap_Client::[get|set]Options() should accept empty string for this option.</p>

